Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,《夜班经理》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的雇主要跻身顶层\N{\rEng}Our paymasters want us at the top table,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,难免要踩着他人的脑袋上位\N{\rEng}we may have to stand on some heads to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.68,0:00:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 我的投资人出资\N{\rEng}Shit. My investors chuck in,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,几亿的资金\N{\rEng}what, a few hundred million?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们得到了一个国家?\N{\rEng}And in return they get a whole country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,铜矿 石油 锂矿 这不就是下金蛋的鹅吗?\N{\rEng}Copper, oil, lithium. I mean, that's the golden goose, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你说不认识泰迪\N{\rEng}You told me you didn't know Teddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要么被引渡到英国 终身监禁 要么帮我打进内部\N{\rEng}Extradition to the UK and a life in prison. Will you get me on the inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他发现 一定会杀了我\N{\rEng}If he finds out, he will kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我六岁的时候我父亲就死了 我亲眼看他们把他扔在门口\N{\rEng}My father died when I was six. I watched them dump him at the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,泰迪是个野性之人 他不适合文明社会\N{\rEng}Teddy's a cowboy. He's not fit for civilised company.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我唯一的儿子和继承人\N{\rEng}Danny is my only son and heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是你偷了货物清单?\N{\rEng}Did you steal the shipment list?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,联系最高法院负责人\N{\rEng}Calling the head of the Supreme Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,康苏埃洛有权下令打开那批货\N{\rEng}Consuelo has the authority to open the shipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,泰迪!嘿!\N{\rEng}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.12,0:00:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,出事了\N{\rEng}Everything's gone wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那个香港投资人... 你还好吗?\N{\rEng}The Hong Kong investor. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...我要他的照片\N{\rEng}I want his picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}亚历克斯古德温
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,亚历克斯古德温 又名安德鲁伯奇\N{\rEng}Alex Goodwin, also known as Andrew Birch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他的名字是乔纳森派恩\N{\rEng}His name is Jonathan Pine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他人在哥伦比亚 他已经盯上我们了\N{\rEng}He's in Colombia, and he's onto our arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我做什么?\N{\rEng}What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他在这里和伦敦都有支援\N{\rEng}He'll have support teams here and in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.80,0:01:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,找出来 处理掉\N{\rEng}Identify them and deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那派恩呢?他现在在哪儿?\N{\rEng}And Pine? Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,把他交给我\N{\rEng}Leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an2\c&H006F35FC\b0\fs19\pos(192,287)}《夜班经理 第二季》\N{\blur0\fnMicrosoft JhengHei\fs15\1c&H62a8eb&\b1}本剧集由{\1c&HFF8000&\fs17\b1}米奇爸爸\N{\fs15\1c&H62a8eb&\b1}基于Amazon官方译文制作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}改根据约翰勒卡雷小说改编
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们继续今天的新闻\N{\rEng}Let's continue with today's news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,塞巴斯蒂安 你有什么消息吗?\N{\rEng}Sebastián, what have you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 胡里奥 是的\N{\rEng}Thanks, Julio. Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,刺杀亚历杭德罗瓜特罗斯的 是一名前游击队员\N{\rEng}The assassin of Alejandro Gualteros is an ex-guerrilla member
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,曾参与过多年的武装战斗\N{\rEng}who spent several years in armed combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,奥克塔维奥佩雷斯目前在逃 被认为是极度危险人物\N{\rEng}Octavio Pérez is on the run and considered highly dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 塞巴斯蒂安 抱歉打断一下...\N{\rEng}Thanks, Sebastián. Sorry to interrupt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还有多远?\N{\rEng}How much further?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,几个小时吧\N{\rEng}A couple hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}哥伦比亚 麦德林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一场针对亚历杭德罗瓜特罗斯的 残酷而冷血的袭击\N{\rEng}This was a brutal and cynical attack against Alejandro Gualteros.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,亚历杭德罗瓜特罗斯为我国的正义 奋斗了一生\N{\rEng}Alejandro tirelessly campaigned for justice in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们目前处于高度警戒状态\N{\rEng}We are at a heightened level of risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因此我会下令提升安保等级\N{\rEng}I am therefore raising security levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}未知号码
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你收到红色警报了吗?\N{\rEng}Did you receive the red flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,收到了 你动身了吗?\N{\rEng}Yeah. Are you moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我正准备动身\N{\rEng}Yeah, I'm just about to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么还没走?现在立刻去机场\N{\rEng}Why haven't you gone already? Get to the airport now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,用我给你的出境通行证 好\N{\rEng}Use the exit parcel provided. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 是我 恐怕我要取消我们的会面了\N{\rEng}Yes. It's me. I'm afraid I'm going to have to cancel our appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我这边有客人\N{\rEng}I have guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把我的调查结果留给你 盖着邮戳的A4横线纸\N{\rEng}I'll leave you my findings. Postmarked, of course. On A4 lined paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,卡拉佩蒂安先生\N{\rEng}Mr Karapetian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是 有什么事吗?\N{\rEng}Yes. How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,需要帮忙吗? 不必 谢谢\N{\rEng}Can I help you? No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他有笔脏钱需要洗白\N{\rEng}He had money that needed cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是他从一家瑞士家族银行偷来的\N{\rEng}He stole it from a Swiss family bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,正好我们需要钱\N{\rEng}It is what we needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,泰迪 我不是早就告诉你...\N{\rEng}Did I not tell you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要那笔该死的钱 不是吗? 或者你有更好的办法吗 混蛋?\N{\rEng}We needed the fucking money, didn't we? Or do you have any better ideas, asshole?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,说英文!\N{\rEng}Speak English!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们听好了\N{\rEng}Let me tell you something about the man you've been dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,和你们打交道的这个人\N{\rEng}Let me tell you something about the man you've been dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是什么瑞士银行家 也不是香港投资人\N{\rEng}He's not a Swiss banker. He's not a Hong Kong investor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,更不会在煤矿乐队里吹短笛\N{\rEng}He doesn't play the piccolo in a colliery band.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他是英国情报特工\N{\rEng}He is a British intelligence agent
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,擅长挖掘别人自己都不知道的信息\N{\rEng}with an indecent habit of getting information people barely knew they had.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人都栽在他这招上\N{\rEng}Many had been susceptible to this gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢打赌罗克珊娜博拉尼奥斯 也逃不掉\N{\rEng}And I'd lay money that Roxana Bolaños could be added to that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢 泰迪? 你是不是也被他套住了?\N{\rEng}What about you, Teddy? Were you susceptible?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思?\N{\rEng}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我 你被他套话了吗?\N{\rEng}Answer the question. Were you susceptible?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没跟马修埃利斯说 他也一无所获\N{\rEng}I told Matthew Ellis nothing. And he has achieved nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,检察官已经死了\N{\rEng}The prosecutor is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会放行货物 交给卡布瑞拉家族\N{\rEng}We will release the cargo and deliver it to the Cabreras.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都按计划进行\N{\rEng}So everything is as we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 计划可是没有差错\N{\rEng}No, the plan was no mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿 乔纳森?\N{\rEng}Where are you, Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定这里安全吗?\N{\rEng}Are you sure it's safe here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,自从我父亲被杀后就没人来过这里\N{\rEng}Mm-hmm. Nobody's been here since my father was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}马丁 我是麦克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}收到新录音 收听
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该听听这个 罗宾逊先生\N{\rEng}You should listen to this, Mr Robinson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们听好了 和你们打交道的这个人\N{\rEng}Let me explain something about the man you've been dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是什么瑞士银行家 也不是香港投资人\N{\rEng}He's not a Swiss banker. He's not a Hong Kong investor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,更不会在煤矿乐队里吹短笛\N{\rEng}He doesn't play the piccolo in a colliery band.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他是英国情报特工 擅长挖掘...\N{\rEng}He is a British intelligence agent with an indecent habit of getting...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫奥克塔维奥 对吗?\N{\rEng}Your name is Octavio, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都叫我塔沃\N{\rEng}People call me Tavo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你有能联系上的家人吗?\N{\rEng}Do you have family you can call?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这会很安全\N{\rEng}You're going to be safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,等我把这事儿解决了\N{\rEng}Until I sort this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗?\N{\rEng}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,别留我和她在一起\N{\rEng}Don't leave me with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是一伙的\N{\rEng}She's one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:11:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 她是我们这边的\N{\rEng}It's all right. She's on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在这等着\N{\rEng}Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么?\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能告诉我是怎么回事?\N{\rEng}You want to tell me what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的那个吉尔伯托汉森\N{\rEng}The man you know as Gilberto Hanson...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个英国军火商\N{\rEng}He's an English arms dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他 有些渊源\N{\rEng}And he and I have... history.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他知道我在这了\N{\rEng}And now he knows I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我得在他找到我之前先去找他\N{\rEng}So, I have to get to him before he gets to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你的团队呢?他们在哪儿? 根本就没什么团队\N{\rEng}What about your team? Where are they? There is no team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉我你有支援的\N{\rEng}You told me you had support.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,其实根本没有\N{\rEng}Well, there's no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就我一个人\N{\rEng}I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那我之前提的保证呢?\N{\rEng}What about the guarantees I asked for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都给不了你\N{\rEng}I can't give you any of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你耍我\N{\rEng}You played me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,为了打入他们内部 我不得不这么做\N{\rEng}I did what was necessary to get on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我把命都交给你了\N{\rEng}I trusted you with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道如果泰迪找到我 他会对我做什么吗?\N{\rEng}Do you have any idea what Teddy will do to me if he finds me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你必须待在这里\N{\rEng}Which is why I need you to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,关掉手机\N{\rEng}Keep your phone off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别让塔沃露面 他们会找他的\N{\rEng}Make sure Tavo stays out of sight. They'll be looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谋杀嫌疑人 罗克珊娜 我说真的\N{\rEng}He's wanted for murder. Roxana, I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在又开始担心塔沃了 是吗\N{\rEng}It's Tavo that we're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 是你选择和那些人合作的\N{\rEng}Listen, you chose to work with these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你清楚你卷进了什么\N{\rEng}You knew what you were getting involved with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我会想办法让你脱身 但别指望我心存感激\N{\rEng}Now, I will get you out of this. But do not ask me to be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你从一开始接近我就是在算计这个\N{\rEng}You planned this from the minute you approached me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你骗了我 故意把我拖下水\N{\rEng}You lied to me. You deliberately compromised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我无处可去\N{\rEng}And now I have nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我骗了你?\N{\rEng}I lied to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那我跟你讲讲瓦利德吧\N{\rEng}Let me tell you about a man called Waleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我的朋友 他有三个孩子\N{\rEng}He was my friend. He had three children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他喜欢打板球 最终流血身亡 死在了我怀里 都是因为你骗了我!\N{\rEng}He loved cricket. And he bled out in my arms because you lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你帮我只有一个原因\N{\rEng}You helped me for one reason and one reason only,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就是为了你自己\N{\rEng}which is to save your own skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得\N{\rEng}I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你也很喜欢我 不是吗?\N{\rEng}you... like my skin, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,待在这\N{\rEng}Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我会回来的\N{\rEng}I'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,随你便吧\N{\rEng}Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也不会求你了\N{\rEng}I will never ask anything of you ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}英国 伦敦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,把我弄这来做什么?\N{\rEng}What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和你聊聊亚历克斯古德温的下落\N{\rEng}I want to talk to you about Alex Goodwin's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,亚历克斯已经死了\N{\rEng}Alex is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 你之前说过\N{\rEng}Yeah, you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你要把他的尸体从西班牙带回来\N{\rEng}You were returning his body from Spain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rEng}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,炸成渣了 是吗?\N{\rEng}Not much of it, was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是昨天在麦德林拍到的\N{\rEng}Taken just yesterday in Medellín.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直在秘密监视这栋房子 巴兹尔\N{\rEng}You've been secretly filming this house, Basil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你还去接近亚当霍利维尔 骗他把手机给你\N{\rEng}And you met Adam Holywell and tricked him into giving you his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,雷克斯葬礼之后 在教堂里 你对我承诺过\N{\rEng}In the church after Rex's funeral you promised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你是绝对忠诚的\N{\rEng}that you were loyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,乔纳森派恩在哪里?\N{\rEng}Where's Jonathan Pine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本不知道你在说什么\N{\rEng}I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,放屁!别骗我\N{\rEng}Bullshit. Don't fucking lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我再问你一遍 乔纳森派恩在哪里?\N{\rEng}I'm gonna ask you again. Where is Jonathan Pine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,查理 我们帮他回忆一下 好吗?\N{\rEng}Charlie. Let's see if we can jog his memory, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,弗里斯基 你能接电话真是太好了\N{\rEng}Frisky. Thank you for answering the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,为了你 做什么都行 老大\N{\rEng}Oh, no. Anything for you, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着法蒂玛就行\N{\rEng}Battle Boy will show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,运气好还能喝瓶啤酒 最近怎么样?\N{\rEng}If you're lucky, you might get a bottle of beer. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是谁?\N{\rEng}Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,家那边的朋友 他们会帮我们找人\N{\rEng}Friends from home. They're gonna help us find your boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:17:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我来就行\N{\rEng}Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不不\N{\rEng}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你来处理货物\N{\rEng}You focus on the shipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,新检察官今早会放行那批货\N{\rEng}The new prosecutor's gonna release the cargo this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你飞去卡塔赫纳 把货从港口运出来\N{\rEng}Fly to Cartagena. Get the cargo out of that port.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,货的事我的手下就能做\N{\rEng}That's transportation. I have boys who can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,泰迪 听着\N{\rEng}Teddy, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,被复仇蒙蔽的人最后只会毁了自己\N{\rEng}A man hell-bent on revenge guarantees only his own demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得专注当下的任务\N{\rEng}You and I have to focus on the task at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,何塞卡布瑞拉 周年日\N{\rEng}José Cabrera, the anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,美洲之王 还记得吗?\N{\rEng}Kings of America, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,接电话\N{\rEng}Answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁?\N{\rEng}Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,让他听电话\N{\rEng}Put him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是让我头大\N{\rEng}Well, you are trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,山顶餐厅\N{\rEng}The hilltop restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我用安德鲁伯奇的名字订了位\N{\rEng}I booked a table under the name of Andrew Birch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,下午一点 一个人来\N{\rEng}1 p.m. Come alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,汉森先生 您的朋友已经到了 抱歉我没来得及清场\N{\rEng}Mr Hanson, your friend is already here. Sorry I couldn't clear the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 别担心 圣地亚哥\N{\rEng}No, no. Don't you worry, Santiago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁是我在伦敦的老同事 是个了不起的人\N{\rEng}Andrew's an old colleague from London. Top man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:20:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那边 谢谢\N{\rEng}Okay, sir. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁\N{\rEng}Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,吉尔伯托\N{\rEng}Gilberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见\N{\rEng}Been too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,您要点些什么吗?\N{\rEng}Can I get you anything, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,两杯你这最好的果汁\N{\rEng}Uh... Two of your delicious juices.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,菜单就免了 我俩都要牛排\N{\rEng}And don't bother with menus. We'll both have the steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我要见血的那种 好的 先生\N{\rEng}And I want to see blood. Sangre! Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我得提醒你一句 这家餐厅是我朋友开的\N{\rEng}I should probably warn you that this place is owned by a pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你要敢乱来 可不会有好下场\N{\rEng}So if you try anything, you will come badly unstuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才选了这里\N{\rEng}That's why I chose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.80,0:21:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你觉得安全\N{\rEng}I wanted you to feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我\N{\rEng}I, on the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,本可以让你在上山的路上 就被一枪爆头\N{\rEng}could have had a bullet put in your skull on the drive up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.60,0:22:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但你没有\N{\rEng}But you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你还得下山呢\N{\rEng}There's always the drive down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.48,0:22:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你老了一些\N{\rEng}You look older.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但我更聪明了\N{\rEng}Yeah. Well, I'm certainly wiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,杰德怎么样?容光焕发吧?\N{\rEng}How's Jed? Glowing, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.32,0:22:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,开罗之后我就没见过她了\N{\rEng}I haven't seen her since Cairo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对她的健康来说也是好事\N{\rEng}Well, that's probably best for her health.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,还有安吉拉伯尔\N{\rEng}And Angela Burr?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉她了吗?\N{\rEng}You've spoken to her about all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,安吉拉伯尔是个懦夫\N{\rEng}Angela Burr is a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这话有点过了吧\N{\rEng}That's a bit harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.04,0:22:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她做出了理性的选择 她骗了我\N{\rEng}She made an informed choice. She lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.16,0:22:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那谁知道你来这了?\N{\rEng}So who knows you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.08,0:22:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没人知道\N{\rEng}Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,胡扯\N{\rEng}Oh, bollocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:23:00.56,Default,,0,0
